dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Larry Price. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Larry. My name is Betty Sanders.
Nice to meet you, Betty. How can I assist you today?
I need to file a new claim. I was involved in an accident yesterday.
I'm sorry to hear that, Betty. Can you provide me with the date and time of the accident?
The accident happened on the twenty-first of September at three thirty in the afternoon.
Thank you, Betty. Could you also verify your policy number and vehicle registration number for me, please?
My policy number is seven eight two four six and the vehicle registration number is C as in Charlie, A as in Alpha, seven zero nine.
Thank you for providing that information, Betty. I will start the claim process for you. Is there anything else you'd like to add before we proceed?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Larry.
You're welcome, Betty. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
You're welcome, Betty. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
